This paper deals with ethical dilemmas faced by agents or coalitions of agents, which is a topic that falls under the domain of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the concept of sacrifice, which is a key aspect of game theory (cs.GT). The paper presents a logical system to describe properties of dilemmas, which is related to the field of logic (cs.LO). The paper also touches upon ethical considerations, which is a topic in ethics and technology (cs.ET). Finally, the paper discusses joint actions of coalitions, which is a topic in multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
